<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-17 13:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3847 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ALA-MAYOR-RETIRE-ART-     07-17 1239
