young prince of Camelot. (Staff, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   KENNEDY-HUFFMAN-COLUMN _ Reactions and thoughts on the Kennedy
plane search by columnist Dale Huffman. (Huffman, Dayton Daily
News)
</P>
<P>
   KENNEDY-NET _ There's no shortage of news on the Kennedy saga on
