<P>
   DIVERSITY-WORKPLACE (Kansas City, Mo.) If one defines workplace
diversity as taco day in the company cafeteria, a sensitivity
seminar for employees or a line in a mission statement about
respecting cultural differences, then everything's up to date in
Kansas City. But if a diverse company is one where management,
